countries because they're not

04:45.652 --> 04:49.523 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
fleeing war. Hundreds gathered
behind gates and barbed-wire

04:49.556 --> 04:53.727 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
fences, shouting at police.
Others taped or even sewed their

04:53.760 --> 04:57.597 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
