nation of Mali today to begin

05:01.434 --> 05:04.838 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
three days of mourning for the
victims of Friday's attack on a

05:04.871 --> 05:08.108 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
luxury hotel there. State
television aired photos of the

05:08.141 --> 05:11.144 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
