violence has killed 20,000

05:42.242 --> 05:46.546 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
people. Voters in Argentina have
ushered in a new era, electing

05:46.580 --> 05:50.417 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
their first conservative
president in 12 years. Last

05:50.450 --> 05:54.054 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
night, Mauricio Macri danced on
stage with his family at his

05:54.087 --> 05:57.390 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Buenos Aires headquarters. The
right-wing mayor of Buenos Aires

05:57.424 --> 06:01.094 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
beat the ruling party's nominee
in a runoff, after promising to

06:01.127 --> 06:03.496 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
boost the economy and fight
corruption. MAURICIO MACRI,

06:03.530 --> 06:05.498 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
President-Elect of Argentina
(through translator): The

06:05.532 --> 06:07.901 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
