want to say to you today as well

06:12.339 --> 06:15.609 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
as to our brothers of Latin
America and to our brothers of

06:15.642 --> 06:18.345 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the world that we want to have
good relationships with all the

06:18.378 --> 06:21.581 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
countries. We want to work with
all of you. GWEN IFILL: Macri

06:21.615 --> 06:24.784 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
