inherits a country with 30

06:24.818 --> 06:28.888 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
percent inflation and stagnant
economic growth. Back in this

06:28.922 --> 06:31.825 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
country, police in New Orleans
are trying to find out what

06:31.858 --> 06:34.828 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
sparked a gun battle in a
crowded city park last night.

06:34.861 --> 06:38.098 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Hundreds had gathered for an
evening block party at a local

06:38.131 --> 06:42.068 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
playground when gunfire rang
out. At least 17 people were

06:42.102 --> 06:45.705 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
wounded in the crossfire. Today,
New Orleans Mayor Mitch Landrieu

06:45.739 --> 06:48.208 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
called on witnesses to come
forward. MITCH LANDRIEU (D),

06:48.241 --> 06:50.210 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Mayor of New Orleans, Louisiana:
Here's the message to the guys

06:50.243 --> 06:53.013 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
