wounds or were grazed by

07:17.570 --> 07:21.341 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
bullets. In business news, the
pharmaceutical giant Pfizer

07:21.374 --> 07:24.344 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
