moving its New York headquarters

07:32.752 --> 07:35.789 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to Dublin, Ireland, where
Allergan is based. The

07:35.822 --> 07:39.225 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
