organization that's expanding

12:36.956 --> 12:41.961 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
its targets beyond Iraq and
Syria. This week, France's

13:13.159 --> 13:18.164 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
president is seeking additional
help from both the U.S. and

13:53.366 --> 13:58.371 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Russia. BARACK OBAMA, President
of the United States: Our

14:29.569 --> 14:34.574 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
