15:05.738 --> 15:10.743 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
yesterday, President Obama
pledged to take the fight to the

15:16.916 --> 15:21.888 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Islamic State. The terror
attacks in Paris, which led to a

15:21.921 --> 15:26.759 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
