53:00.244 --> 53:02.212 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
education. CARIN MALMER,
Teacher: Parents have a really

53:02.246 --> 53:06.183 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
important role in the child's
