53:40.017 --> 53:42.586 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
English-language learners. APRIL
BROWN: English-language learners

53:42.619 --> 53:46.023 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
like Charlie, who Espinoza says
